==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Immaterially
<hw>Im`ma*te"ri*al*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>In an
immaterial manner; without matter or corporeal substance.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>In an unimportant manner or degree.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Immaterialness</ent>⟦br⟧
